lead_paragraph: An Italian prosecutor has appealed against future Chelsea coach Antonio Conte's acquittal earlier this year in a 2011 match-fixing scandal, a legal source said on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Italy Prosecutor Appeals Antonio Conte's Match-Fixing Acquittal
